      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 Lexus RX 350 in a sophisticated Mica Nightfall finish. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and is in excellent mechanical health. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you will find minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014standard signs of careful use. Inside, the Parchment leather interior is remarkably clean; the seats are firm and free of any punctures or stains, with only light softening on the driver\u2019s entry bolster. All onboard technology, including the navigation system, heated/ventilated seats, and the premium audio suite, operates perfectly. Under the hood, the V6 engine runs quietly and the transmission shifts seamlessly. It has a full service history, with the most recent oil change and multi-point inspection completed just two months ago. The tires are matching Michelins with plenty of life left. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that offers a quiet, luxurious ride and is ready for its next long-term owner.",
